  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to investigate the association of obesity with arterial blood
      pressure, atherosclerosis, target organ damage (heart, arteries, kidney) and insulin
      resistance in children and young adolescents.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
